{"tid":1283791,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"共臣榜MV資料搜集","createTime":"2019-07-04T02:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T05:15:02.000Z","uid":266563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d717a970b8bdba1aee3ed3d76368179e55b4eb90","tid":1283791,"uid":266563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:18:11.000Z","msg":"多得咁多位巴絲努力 共臣榜填詞完畢<br />\n<br />\n而家我想做個MV推上YouTube 請大家比啲資料片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n何君，率眾妖害人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n白：<span style=\"color: red;\">港共將卒從今定 黑警朝朝墮草萊<br />\n太上維尼新帝敕令 「五方鬼王 來受命耳 」此乃「共臣榜」</span><br />\n<br />\n* 男:<span style=\"color: red;\">林媽　推送中賣民　人死　不理何殘忍<br />\n無恥　擁護中共行　蒼天恨<br />\n蛇心 甘殺子滅民 人渣 奸笑提民憤<br />\n藍絲　通處打柒人　犬不聞</span><br />\n女:<span style=\"color: red;\">智耗盡 貪佢派個一兩蚊</span><br />\n男:<span style=\"color: red;\">冇信義 恰港人 李卡超 分化警和民</span><br />\n女:<span style=\"color: red;\">耍陰招 卑鄙柒和笨</span><br />\n合:<span style=\"color: red;\">建制派 禍城又殃民</span><br />\n男:<span style=\"color: red;\">廢物 有樹根 (割蓆 割樹根)</span><br />\n<br />\n* 男: <span style=\"color: red;\">盧狗 率眾犬害人 孽瘤 歪理難容忍<br />\n梁君 只會奶共臣 屎忽痕<br />\n肥芬 跟政府共沉　何妖 終被雷霆轟<br />\n齊心 隊冧蔣麗芸 真&middot;低能</span><br />\n女:<span style=\"color: red;\">票耗盡 慧琼美娟失了身</span><br />\n男:<span style=\"color: red;\">正契弟 欺天地　說兩制　反智抑良民</span><br />\n女:<span style=\"color: red;\">記老母 一國至為實</span><br />\n合:<span style=\"color: red;\">建制派 禍城又殃民</span><br />\n男:<span style=\"color: red;\">廢物 有樹根 (割蓆 割樹根)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家集氣 推上youtube</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為方便整理 格式如下<br />\n<br />\n[link] [title] [開始時間］[重點］</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dXLQUUI9whg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdXLQUUI9whg&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=a87cf85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dXLQUUI9whg</a> 陶桀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nu99jP4URdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNu99jP4URdU&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=b2fdb702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nu99jP4URdU</a> 69<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vzNsIGtDhdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvzNsIGtDhdA&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=542db426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vzNsIGtDhdA</a> 618林鄭記者會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lUiVLW9CzmU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlUiVLW9CzmU&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=cd25d61d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lUiVLW9CzmU</a> 李超記會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2lQJtsd6b14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2lQJtsd6b14&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e71d930a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2lQJtsd6b14</a> 626 警總<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UQxHIVHJJx8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUQxHIVHJJx8&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=25d7eb0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UQxHIVHJJx8</a> 成立獨委會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vpb5cAy3Bww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVpb5cAy3Bww&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=fc0b5fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vpb5cAy3Bww</a> 619立會質詢 1:25:40 李超投警科"},{"pid":"be9bf3af6f47e8e3ed8e531ee356609ce9a7d24d","tid":1283791,"uid":266563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e